These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, soccer, snowboarding, water-polo
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, chess, photography, reading
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, cain, chaman, pall-mall
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, fisherman, engineer, architect
1. the cain-smoker is the person who's hobby is reading##1
2. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
3. the cain-smoker is the mechanic##1
4. the architect is on the left of the mechanic##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the engineer is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Sport   | soccer | water-polo   | golf  | snowboarding  |
| Hobby   | chess    | reading    | video-games      | photography    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | cain | chaman | vegafina |
| Job     | architect  | mechanic       | fisherman    | engineer     |

