.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, skateboard, boat, jet-ski
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, july, october, may
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, bridge, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, salsa, hip-hop
1. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person playing canasta is the fan disco##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person playing bridge and the fan country##2
6. the fan hip-hop is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person playing canasta##2
7. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport         | jet-ski | skateboard    | boat  | car    |
| Birthday   | april      | july  | may  | october |
| Game           | canasta      | bridge       | domino      | scrabble       |
| Music-Genre         | disco    | hip-hop | salsa | country |

