City: london, venice, nizza, miami
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, fanta, juice
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, september, july
1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person traveling to miami##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
8. the owner of the fish is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to miami##2
9. the person traveling to nizza is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking iced-tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Pet        | turtle | frog     | fish   | guinea-pig     |
| City       | venice   | london   | nizza | miami |
| Beverage         | water   | fanta | juice       | iced-tea    |
| Birthday   | september    | december | may  | july    |

