 7. the person playing snooker is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
